,"msg":"<blockquote>就算個男鐘意你都唔會接受你<br />\n因為佢會冇左一大班朋友</blockquote><br />\n我知 所以我無諗過我同佢有可能 <br />\n我淨係想同佢傾下計 相處下就已經好開心<br />\n最重要係見唔到佢女朋友係到就得"},{"pid":"9559f34edc79dff25f4245f2ce73b69010e21268","tid":39624,"uid":23902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:04:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有請巨乳人妻</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}